Photo Dump: Hanging with some of my Grammy Award-Winning friends🏆
If these walls could talk… #TwelveStudios

Raise your hand if you ever spent the night at @twelvemusic lol🙋🏻‍♀️🙄🤣

But on a serious musical note, this studio wasn’t successful bc of how high-tech the equipment was or the size of the rooms, it was successful bc of the energy that was intentionally set & the community it created (on-purpose). I carefully curated the hand-selected group of talent & executives that laid the foundation for this magical space: @polowdadon in Blueprint, @raydaniels @therontheron_ & @rcity in Adele, @kawanprather for @atlanticrecords in Thriller and all the talent I developed & managed like now Grammy Award-winner @spillmyink in Purple Rain. That’s how we opened the doors in 2012 which then lead to @richforever @untouchablemmg @la_reid @epicrecords @ghazi @empire @aaronareid @itschubbiebaby @pierrebourne @fuse808mafia @stonii @tm88 @urdjuice @blancobrown @jozzy @therealkapg @only1mike_d @javarsaidpickupthatbag @deshawnkennedy @cheezebeatz @nonstopdahitman @anonxmousking @vincephillipsesq @hollywoodserge_ @vinnykumar and a multitude of upcoming & legendary talent and engineers like @cozilla @darth__moon @rastapapii @i_am_thomas_j @producedbyposta @randemword @cliffordhenson @sneakabeat @theoryproducer @skitzpittz @guitarboymusic1 Burroughs, Richard & Cat that called Twelve their ATL home🏆

Not only did we build creative talent but we nurtured business professionals like @spittywill @allenmichael.aguilar @jososaidso @ambergrimes @jvrdrvp @cizzurp215 @kandisknight @louiecrackk @don_veedoe @y5.mad @bunduke_ @janaymariejames and the women that managed the operation starting with @worldofkrys then @abfromkc2 & finally @lindexia 

Honorable mention to @mylovejourney_ who helped me keep things afloat until @ceosaad & @bigapelo took over in 2019

I think we had well over 300 interns throughout the 12 years & served too many Otis Spunkmeyer cookies to count🙃

I typically don’t write this much but I really wanted to reflect & appreciate this moment🙏🏼

We will always be one big extended family and I’m honored to have been a small piece of all your careers & lives🫶🏼 #TwelveForLife #TwelveStudios

☀️My Morning Routine is Essential☀️

It sets the tone for my day. Waking up early to have time to myself to gather my thoughts & intentions lays the groundwork for how the rest of my day is handled and achieved☕️

Some of my morning routine includes meditation, affirmations, exercise & trying to tackle the hardest task on my to do list✅I make an effort to spend the first 2 hours of my day without interacting on any social media.

And here comes daylight savings messing with our routine again🤪What is one thing you make sure to do every morning to keep your mental health aligned?

Standing On Business🫡

Having a solid support system of trusted colleagues is a major key to success in any industry, but that doesn’t mean you should treat their opinions as gospel! 

If you TRULY believe in an idea (especially when it’s YOUR brand/business), trust your intuition, put it into action, and take full responsibility for any W’s or L’s that come from it.

The only “wrong” path is regret.
